reviews.name: El Sabroso Guacachip Tortilla Chips, 12 oz (Pack of 12)
reviews.reviewText: I always bought the small bag from 7 eleven. I was so excited when I saw I was able to order a whole box of them. I brought some to my office and all my co-workers and I cannot stop eating these. These chips are soooo good. :)
reviews.title: These chips are delicious!!!!!!!

reviews.name: El Sabroso Guacachip Tortilla Chips, 12 oz (Pack of 12)
reviews.reviewText: The taste is amazing, im glad I found them here. The box came undamaged and the bigs were intact and not crushed or broken. The only downside to my experience is the expiration is 3 months away. Not a big deal for one or two bags but 12 huge bags and its a little of an issue. Overall I am satisfied with them.
reviews.title: I love these chips.
